
## Netlify redirect rules for domain migration and canonical URLs

# Force HTTPS and canonical domain (non-www)
http://ghataksportsacademy.com/* https://ghataksportsacademy.com/:splat 301!
https://www.ghataksportsacademy.com/* https://ghataksportsacademy.com/:splat 301!
http://www.ghataksportsacademy.com/* https://ghataksportsacademy.com/:splat 301!

# Force 301 redirect from old Netlify domain to production domain
https://ghatakgsai.netlify.app/* https://ghataksportsacademy.com/:splat 301!
http://ghatakgsai.netlify.app/* https://ghataksportsacademy.com/:splat 301!
https://www.ghatakgsai.netlify.app/* https://ghataksportsacademy.com/:splat 301!
http://www.ghatakgsai.netlify.app/* https://ghataksportsacademy.com/:splat 301!

# SPA fallback - must be last
/* /index.html 200
